.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626245bc231fc70d3d48e806973f4b2c52520afb","tid":733104,"uid":15184,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"細個同屋企人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而加諗返起個畫面都覺得溫馨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打喚醒左我呢段回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ea94d7102b3e05aa68f6cd8c3578d2a2739a1d","tid":733104,"uid":28061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb804e3a27880098b70b9b4ff2b4797c9c847337","tid":733104,"uid":146243,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"幼稚園去過<br />\n<br />\n有個互射海綿波好好玩 好有印象我描住個阿姨 個波飛埋去打正佢塊面 個感覺好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T22:03:58.000Z","msg":"我呢排諗起呢個射波波場面<br />\n但又醒唔起係邊到<br />\n原來係小熊國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f1172aa87ec8abb88485cf51552805a41bcb9a","tid":733104,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T22:07:53.000Z","msg":"整左隻bear"},{"pid":"700b64c8b44562170ae9cd50a3414288b781bf16","tid":733104,"uid":143018,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T22:14:10.000Z","msg":"好細個去過一次，個場有兩隻成層樓高嘅熊啤啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又有啲熊仔故事場景睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜乜都好L貴，所以淨係可以影吓相，冇得玩+唔畀買嘢...睇住其他小朋友玩 、join story time 坐喺大熊仔腳下聽故事、排隊整屬於自己嘅熊仔、買靚衫畀熊仔著...超羨慕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5387a9d6981b7b3fb8b7398709fa2af3e5a20ee3","tid":733104,"uid":30417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T23:45:11.000Z","msg":"整過熊仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c973161418e0e11b4572e2efd7f2138b8588ef0d","tid":733104,"uid":20816,"like":0,"